# `@plop/logger`

Shared `pino` logger instance.

## Conventions

- Prefer structured logs (objects) over string concatenation.
- Do not log secrets (tokens, keys, raw cookies, Authorization headers).
- Import the shared logger from `@plop/logger` instead of creating new instances in apps.

